cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.CE, cs.ETM 

This paper deals with the problem of managing virtual machines in datacenters to reduce brown energy consumption by utilizing renewable energy. This involves optimizing the communication between datacenters and the use of renewable energy sources. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also deals with datacenters and their energy consumption, which falls under the category of cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also involves optimization and decision-making, which can be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of renewable energy sources and the optimization of energy consumption can also be categorized under cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) and cs.ETM (Emerging Technologies).
